&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;content-p&#34;&gt;The website you&amp;rsquo;re reading right now!  I tried to do things a bit differently with this website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In building this website, I had three main goals.  I wanted the site to:&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;have understandable source code,&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;be self-sufficient, and&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;be the &lt;a href=&#34;https://hackernoon.com/10-things-i-learned-making-the-fastest-site-in-the-world-18a0e1cdf4a7&#34;&gt;fastest site in the world&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;p class=&#34;content-p&#34;&gt;Here is my analysis of how well I managed to meet these goals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
